[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":367},["ShallowReactive",2],{"header-locale:\u002Fen\u002Fdocker\u002F2023\u002F01\u002F29\u002Fstep-by-step-docker-push-to-docker-hub\u002F":3,"page:\u002Fen\u002Fdocker\u002F2023\u002F01\u002F29\u002Fstep-by-step-docker-push-to-docker-hub\u002F":4,"alt:\u002Fen\u002Fdocker\u002F2023\u002F01\u002F29\u002Fstep-by-step-docker-push-to-docker-hub\u002F":3,"prev-next:\u002Fen\u002Fdocker\u002F2023\u002F01\u002F29\u002Fstep-by-step-docker-push-to-docker-hub\u002F":347,"related:\u002Fen\u002Fdocker\u002F2023\u002F01\u002F29\u002Fstep-by-step-docker-push-to-docker-hub\u002F":356},"\u002Fdocker\u002F20230129\u002F2952136309\u002F",{"id":5,"title":6,"abbrlink":7,"altUrl":3,"body":8,"category":328,"date":329,"description":330,"extension":331,"lang":332,"meta":333,"navigation":334,"path":335,"readingMinutes":336,"seo":337,"standalone":338,"stem":339,"tags":340,"tldr":343,"updated":344,"url":345,"__hash__":346},"content\u002Fen\u002FDocker\u002Fstep-by-step-docker-push-to-docker-hub.md","(9) Step-by-Step Docker — Pushing Your Image to Docker Hub","4048063305",{"type":9,"value":10,"toc":323},"minimark",[11,16,20,24,27,38,41,64,71,83,89,99,102,117,120,126,157,160,192,199,215,224,230,233,246,262,268,271,277,284,290,296,299,306,309,319],[12,13,15],"h2",{"id":14},"intro","Intro",[17,18,19],"p",{},"Next up — let's push the Docker Image we built earlier to Docker Hub so we can use it from anywhere.",[12,21,23],{"id":22},"pushing-your-image-to-docker-hub","Pushing your Image to Docker Hub",[17,25,26],{},"We built an Image in the \"Building a Docker Image\" post. Let's use that for this walkthrough.",[17,28,29,30,37],{},"First, make sure you have a Docker Hub account. If not, register at ",[31,32,36],"a",{"href":33,"rel":34},"https:\u002F\u002Fhub.docker.com\u002F",[35],"nofollow","Docker Hub",".",[17,39,40],{},"Then in your terminal, log in:",[42,43,48],"pre",{"className":44,"code":45,"language":46,"meta":47,"style":47},"language-bash shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","docker login\n","bash","",[49,50,51],"code",{"__ignoreMap":47},[52,53,56,60],"span",{"class":54,"line":55},"line",1,[52,57,59],{"class":58},"s_sBn","docker",[52,61,63],{"class":62},"sTRMh"," login\n",[17,65,66,67,70],{},"Once you're logged in, we can push. First, confirm your Image name with ",[49,68,69],{},"docker images",":",[42,72,74],{"className":44,"code":73,"language":46,"meta":47,"style":47},"docker images\n",[49,75,76],{"__ignoreMap":47},[52,77,78,80],{"class":54,"line":55},[52,79,59],{"class":58},[52,81,82],{"class":62}," images\n",[17,84,85],{},[86,87],"img",{"alt":69,"src":88},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fdocker\u002F%E4%B8%80%E6%AD%A5%E6%AD%A5%E6%8E%8C%E6%8F%A1%E5%9F%BA%E7%A4%8E-Docker\u002FzV65bfw.png",[17,90,91,92,95,96,37],{},"Our Image is ",[49,93,94],{},"docker-express-example",", tag ",[49,97,98],{},"v1",[17,100,101],{},"Now push:",[42,103,105],{"className":44,"code":104,"language":46,"meta":47,"style":47},"docker push docker-express-example:v1\n",[49,106,107],{"__ignoreMap":47},[52,108,109,111,114],{"class":54,"line":55},[52,110,59],{"class":58},[52,112,113],{"class":62}," push",[52,115,116],{"class":62}," docker-express-example:v1\n",[17,118,119],{},"You'll probably hit this error:",[17,121,122],{},[86,123],{"alt":124,"src":125},"docker push error","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fdocker\u002F%E4%B8%80%E6%AD%A5%E6%AD%A5%E6%8E%8C%E6%8F%A1%E5%9F%BA%E7%A4%8E-Docker\u002FvFO857j.png",[42,127,129],{"className":44,"code":128,"language":46,"meta":47,"style":47},"denied: requested access to the resource is denied\n",[49,130,131],{"__ignoreMap":47},[52,132,133,136,139,142,145,148,151,154],{"class":54,"line":55},[52,134,135],{"class":58},"denied:",[52,137,138],{"class":62}," requested",[52,140,141],{"class":62}," access",[52,143,144],{"class":62}," to",[52,146,147],{"class":62}," the",[52,149,150],{"class":62}," resource",[52,152,153],{"class":62}," is",[52,155,156],{"class":62}," denied\n",[17,158,159],{},"That's because the Image isn't tagged with your account namespace. Tag it with your Docker Hub username first:",[42,161,163],{"className":44,"code":162,"language":46,"meta":47,"style":47},"docker tag docker-express-example:v1 \u003Cyour-docker-hub-account>\u002Fdocker-express-example:v1\n",[49,164,165],{"__ignoreMap":47},[52,166,167,169,172,175,179,182,186,189],{"class":54,"line":55},[52,168,59],{"class":58},[52,170,171],{"class":62}," tag",[52,173,174],{"class":62}," docker-express-example:v1",[52,176,178],{"class":177},"sWyjQ"," \u003C",[52,180,181],{"class":62},"your-docker-hub-accoun",[52,183,185],{"class":184},"sMAXC","t",[52,187,188],{"class":177},">",[52,190,191],{"class":62},"\u002Fdocker-express-example:v1\n",[17,193,194,195,198],{},"My username is ",[49,196,197],{},"hsiangfeng",", so for me it'd be:",[42,200,202],{"className":44,"code":201,"language":46,"meta":47,"style":47},"docker tag docker-express-example:v1 hsiangfeng\u002Fdocker-express-example:v1\n",[49,203,204],{"__ignoreMap":47},[52,205,206,208,210,212],{"class":54,"line":55},[52,207,59],{"class":58},[52,209,171],{"class":62},[52,211,174],{"class":62},[52,213,214],{"class":62}," hsiangfeng\u002Fdocker-express-example:v1\n",[17,216,217,218,220,221,37],{},"Run ",[49,219,69],{}," again and you'll see a new entry: ",[49,222,223],{},"hsiangfeng\u002Fdocker-express-example",[17,225,226],{},[86,227],{"alt":228,"src":229},"docker images updated","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fdocker\u002F%E4%B8%80%E6%AD%A5%E6%AD%A5%E6%8E%8C%E6%8F%A1%E5%9F%BA%E7%A4%8E-Docker\u002Fi7rJhFo.png",[17,231,232],{},"You might excitedly try:",[42,234,236],{"className":44,"code":235,"language":46,"meta":47,"style":47},"docker push hsiangfeng\u002Fdocker-express-example:v1\n",[49,237,238],{"__ignoreMap":47},[52,239,240,242,244],{"class":54,"line":55},[52,241,59],{"class":58},[52,243,113],{"class":62},[52,245,214],{"class":62},[17,247,248,249,252,253,258,259,261],{},"And still get ",[49,250,251],{},"denied: requested access to the resource is denied",". That's because there's one more step — you need to create a Repository on Docker Hub first. Head to ",[31,254,257],{"href":255,"rel":256},"https:\u002F\u002Fhub.docker.com\u002Frepositories\u002F",[35],"your repositories"," and click \"Create repository\". The name should match your Image name, so ",[49,260,94],{}," here.",[17,263,264],{},[86,265],{"alt":266,"src":267},"Create repository","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fdocker\u002F%E4%B8%80%E6%AD%A5%E6%AD%A5%E6%8E%8C%E6%8F%A1%E5%9F%BA%E7%A4%8E-Docker\u002F5qeqhMI.png",[17,269,270],{},"After creation:",[17,272,273],{},[86,274],{"alt":275,"src":276},"Repository created","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fdocker\u002F%E4%B8%80%E6%AD%A5%E6%AD%A5%E6%8E%8C%E6%8F%A1%E5%9F%BA%E7%A4%8E-Docker\u002FaNpvqiu.png",[17,278,279,280,283],{},"Now ",[49,281,282],{},"docker push hsiangfeng\u002Fdocker-express-example:v1"," and you'll see the push succeed.",[17,285,286],{},[86,287],{"alt":288,"src":289},"Push success","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fdocker\u002F%E4%B8%80%E6%AD%A5%E6%AD%A5%E6%8E%8C%E6%8F%A1%E5%9F%BA%E7%A4%8E-Docker\u002FehtkcmT.png",[17,291,292],{},[86,293],{"alt":294,"src":295},"Push success on Docker Hub","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fdocker\u002F%E4%B8%80%E6%AD%A5%E6%AD%A5%E6%8E%8C%E6%8F%A1%E5%9F%BA%E7%A4%8E-Docker\u002Fo2g5IBK.png",[17,297,298],{},"Pretty straightforward, right?",[17,300,301,302,305],{},"Later, on another computer or on someone else's machine, you can ",[49,303,304],{},"docker pull hsiangfeng\u002Fdocker-express-example:v1"," to pull this Image — since it's public.",[17,307,308],{},"This post's short, so that's it.",[17,310,311,312,314,315,318],{},"(If your commands look right but you keep getting ",[49,313,251],{},", you probably forgot to ",[49,316,317],{},"docker login",".)",[320,321,322],"sty